**AVOID GENERIC AI AESTHETICS** - Skip Inter, Arial, Helvetica. These signal amateur execution.

**DISTINCTIVE FONT COMBINATIONS:**
- Trajan Pro + Minion Pro (classical luxury)
- Futura + Times New Roman (unexpected contrast)
- Custom variable fonts with weight animations

